WEBVTT

01:36.990 --> 01:40.900
[The Best Thing]

01:41.390 --> 01:48.479
[Episode 25： Pinellia]
[Pungent, damp in nature, toxic, dries dampness, transforms phlegm, redirects rebellious qi to stop vomiting, and dissolves stagnation and nodules.]

01:49.680 --> 01:51.759
Pens are hot commodities in hospitals.

01:52.789 --> 01:54.000
This pen is so unique.

01:54.560 --> 01:55.680
I'd like to see

01:55.700 --> 01:58.090
who's been taking them from me all this time.

01:58.640 --> 02:00.230
But this one is so cute.

02:00.230 --> 02:01.510
Are you sure you want this one?

02:02.760 --> 02:03.920
I think it suits me well.

02:04.870 --> 02:05.430
Don't you think so?

02:07.860 --> 02:09.340
I feel it suits you very well.

02:10.310 --> 02:11.030
It's mine now?

02:11.170 --> 02:11.770
Okay.

02:16.210 --> 02:17.610
What are these?

02:17.640 --> 02:18.640
Your lesson plan?

02:19.400 --> 02:22.710
Yes, I'm going to teach next semester.

02:23.120 --> 02:24.960
The principal asked me to come up with a few alternative course options.

02:25.190 --> 02:26.750
So I need to refer to

02:26.750 --> 02:28.150
my senior colleagues' lesson plans recently.

02:29.240 --> 02:30.400
Yes.

02:30.720 --> 02:32.829
You'll be Teacher He in the future.

02:34.840 --> 02:37.120
So you'll be working at the hospital

02:37.120 --> 02:38.560
while going back to teach.

02:38.560 --> 02:39.840
Won't that be too exhausting?

02:42.140 --> 02:43.140
It's better to be busy.

02:43.570 --> 02:46.220
Otherwise, when you go abroad, I'll have nothing to do

02:46.250 --> 02:47.490
except sitting at home and thinking about you.

02:47.970 --> 02:49.780
I'll have holidays, you know.

02:49.810 --> 02:51.530
As soon as I have a break, I'll come back to see you.

02:52.250 --> 02:54.010
Teacher He will be very busy.

02:54.040 --> 02:55.160
You have time to come back

02:55.180 --> 02:56.740
but Teacher He might not have time to see you.

02:58.000 --> 02:58.750
Okay.

03:01.560 --> 03:02.800
I'm just kidding.

03:04.050 --> 03:05.360
Study hard.

03:05.390 --> 03:08.110
I'll see if I can save up some annual leave to visit you abroad.

03:11.120 --> 03:11.680
By the way,

03:12.310 --> 03:13.030
you should quickly prepare

03:13.030 --> 03:14.870
all the materials needed for your visa

03:14.870 --> 03:15.840
and submit your application as soon as possible.

03:16.120 --> 03:17.840
In case there are any issues later,

03:17.840 --> 03:19.000
you can prepare again.

03:20.630 --> 03:21.870
I got it, Teacher He.

03:21.870 --> 03:22.910
You're so naggy.

03:38.630 --> 03:38.910
Here.

03:39.579 --> 03:40.350
Cheers.

03:40.510 --> 03:42.600
Cherish every bubble tea.

03:42.710 --> 03:44.610
In the future, you can drink the bubble tea I develop.

03:45.440 --> 03:48.110
I think you should make eight-treasure congee in the future.

03:50.000 --> 03:52.470
Sure, I'll develop new products then.

03:54.800 --> 03:55.280
What's wrong?

03:58.390 --> 04:00.320
A regular customer told me

04:00.340 --> 04:02.450
to book a villa for them.

04:02.790 --> 04:05.390
It has to be low-key and secluded.

04:06.140 --> 04:06.910
And then?

04:09.080 --> 04:09.960
Xiangya.

04:10.330 --> 04:11.600
This man

04:11.830 --> 04:13.850
is the male lead of the drama you were watching, right?

04:15.020 --> 04:16.070
He's the one visiting?

04:16.510 --> 04:17.750
Did he say if it's a private trip

04:17.750 --> 04:19.160
or if it's for work?

04:19.360 --> 04:20.240
Probably private.

04:20.240 --> 04:21.430
He only booked one.

04:21.430 --> 04:21.950
Who is it?

04:21.950 --> 04:22.950
Let me have a look too.

04:26.430 --> 04:28.720
Maybe he was too tired from filming his last project.

04:28.720 --> 04:30.920
So he came here to relax and unwind.

04:32.480 --> 04:34.310
Or he might have taken on some mysterious job

04:34.330 --> 04:35.370
that he can't disclose.

05:12.070 --> 05:12.900
Sir,

05:14.260 --> 05:17.380
please keep your room key and ID safe.

05:25.740 --> 05:31.260
♫The returning wild geese in rows feel like the signals you send♫

05:31.280 --> 05:36.860
♫The twilight glow, tinted with warmth, feels like your embrace♫

05:37.230 --> 05:43.250
♫The evening breeze sways my hair, like your gentle touch wrapping around me♫

05:42.700 --> 05:43.430
Thank you.

05:43.280 --> 05:52.640
♫The future can only rely on the beauty of imagination♫

06:09.120 --> 06:10.990
It was this drama you watched?

06:11.870 --> 06:12.950
He has huge eyes

06:12.950 --> 06:14.140
and long eyelashes.

06:14.510 --> 06:16.550
He even has a tall nose bridge too.

06:16.550 --> 06:18.020
How is his nose bridge so tall?

06:18.020 --> 06:19.430
His lips are so sexy.

06:23.550 --> 06:24.820
Most importantly,

06:25.190 --> 06:25.900
I think he

06:25.900 --> 06:28.190
really understands good food and understands me.

06:28.190 --> 06:29.400
Really?

06:31.820 --> 06:34.670
Why can't employees take photos with them?

06:34.670 --> 06:36.260
I should have quit earlier if I had known.

06:36.480 --> 06:37.630
You should have called me then.

06:37.630 --> 06:38.750
I could have taken the photo for you.

06:39.310 --> 06:40.190
I missed it.

06:41.070 --> 06:42.110
Do you know he was also very sexy

06:42.110 --> 06:43.460
in another film?

06:43.460 --> 06:44.430
Which film? Which film?

06:45.490 --> 06:46.890
What did she just say?

06:47.700 --> 06:49.020
Who doesn't know how to eat?

06:49.020 --> 06:49.870
Exactly.

06:49.870 --> 06:51.070
You even know how to make medicinal cuisine.

06:51.070 --> 06:51.630
Exactly.

06:51.990 --> 06:53.580
And isn't being 188 cm tall quite common?

06:53.580 --> 06:55.240
Yeah, we're even 190 cm tall.

06:55.670 --> 06:56.190
You're so noisy!

06:57.380 --> 06:58.140
Go and cook.

06:59.460 --> 07:00.140
Alright.

07:00.140 --> 07:00.580
Let's go cook.

07:00.580 --> 07:01.220
Come on, let's go.

07:01.990 --> 07:02.550
We're going to cook.

07:04.070 --> 07:04.810
And then?

07:05.070 --> 07:06.220
Then he just...

07:31.290 --> 07:33.020
Why did you start watching this?

07:35.950 --> 07:37.580
I'm just casually studying it.

07:42.070 --> 07:43.140
Well,

07:43.670 --> 07:45.110
what did you find out?

07:46.340 --> 07:49.260
The female lead is really beautiful.

08:03.590 --> 08:05.230
She is very beautiful.

08:06.070 --> 08:07.020
And then?

08:10.110 --> 08:11.140
I...

08:12.270 --> 08:13.560
should talk less.

08:16.310 --> 08:17.700
You can continue watching.

08:17.870 --> 08:18.900
I'm going to get a drink.

09:00.340 --> 09:05.990
♫The returning wild geese in rows feel like the signals you send♫

09:06.020 --> 09:11.590
♫The twilight glow, tinted with warmth, feels like your embrace♫

09:12.380 --> 09:13.190
Oh my!

09:17.300 --> 09:18.350
What are you doing?

09:19.280 --> 09:20.190
I...

09:21.150 --> 09:22.460
I was just walking around.

09:41.340 --> 09:42.070
Hello, sir.

09:42.070 --> 09:43.220
Please sign here.

09:51.620 --> 09:52.220
Thank you.

09:52.220 --> 09:53.790
We hope you enjoyed your stay.

09:53.980 --> 09:54.670
Thank you.

11:36.210 --> 11:37.510
[For Fan's Study Abroad]

11:38.220 --> 11:39.550
Even if we agree,

11:39.550 --> 11:42.100
applying to study abroad requires a ton of paperwork.

11:42.460 --> 11:43.550
Do you even have time?

11:43.550 --> 11:44.550
Do you have the energy for it?

11:45.070 --> 11:46.220
What after you finish studying abroad?

11:46.220 --> 11:47.950
If you do come back to work,

11:47.950 --> 11:49.550
you'll have to start job-hunting.

11:49.550 --> 11:50.980
At that time, given your age,

11:50.980 --> 11:53.390
every company will consider your

11:53.390 --> 11:53.980
dating,

11:53.980 --> 11:54.670
marriage,

11:54.670 --> 11:55.220
childbirth,

11:55.220 --> 11:57.670
maternity leave, and a series of related issues.

13:18.860 --> 13:19.620
Ms. Liu,

13:21.450 --> 13:23.170
welcome home. You must be tired.

13:24.880 --> 13:26.040
Are your medical examination results out?

13:28.910 --> 13:30.150
It doesn't happen that quickly.

13:30.580 --> 13:33.060
The doctor said everything looks healthy.

13:34.220 --> 13:36.310
When will the complete report be available?

13:36.310 --> 13:37.620
I want to show it to He Suye.

13:37.980 --> 13:39.220
It will take several days.

13:39.220 --> 13:40.210
Not so fast.

13:40.980 --> 13:41.790
Alright.

13:42.580 --> 13:44.550
Are you hungry? You didn't eat before going out this morning.

13:44.550 --> 13:45.670
I'll go make you some food.

13:45.980 --> 13:47.500
I've always been the one cooking for you.

13:47.500 --> 13:48.900
Since when did I need you to cook?

13:49.100 --> 13:50.100
Go back to your room and wait.

13:50.740 --> 13:51.820
Mm, okay then.

13:52.070 --> 13:53.820
Then I want to eat dumplings.

13:54.880 --> 13:55.720
Call me when it's ready.

14:16.150 --> 14:17.550
It's not easy to create lesson plans, is it?

14:18.030 --> 14:19.580
You must be crazy.

14:20.190 --> 14:22.190
The hospital has a five-day workweek,

14:22.310 --> 14:23.520
and you go to the clinic on Saturdays.

14:23.700 --> 14:25.370
At the same time, you have to conduct research

14:25.650 --> 14:28.430
and find time to teach in school.

14:28.950 --> 14:30.190
People who don't know,

14:30.740 --> 14:32.310
might think you're single.

14:33.820 --> 14:36.270
Are you single because you're too free?

14:37.430 --> 14:38.190
How offensive of you.

14:38.910 --> 14:39.740
That's too hurtful.

14:40.580 --> 14:41.500
I think I'm the kind of person...

14:41.500 --> 14:42.310
Dr. Song,

14:42.730 --> 14:44.220
could you please sign this?

14:49.150 --> 14:50.030
Let me use this.

15:05.490 --> 15:06.390
Can I borrow a pen?

15:07.390 --> 15:09.270
A pen given by someone else is different, huh?

15:09.590 --> 15:10.830
Mine was also given by someone else.

15:10.850 --> 15:12.970
Hurry up, thanks.

15:17.910 --> 15:18.740
He,

15:19.190 --> 15:21.250
I'd like you to take a look at my medical examination report.

15:21.580 --> 15:23.030
May I know when will you be free?

15:23.340 --> 15:24.620
It's up to you, what do you think?

15:24.620 --> 15:26.270
I can look at it at home after work.

15:27.520 --> 15:30.160
With my conditions, I shouldn't be single.

15:31.220 --> 15:31.700
Could it be because...

15:31.700 --> 15:34.150
If you're not busy, I can come to the hospital to find you.

15:34.920 --> 15:36.170
I think I still

15:36.810 --> 15:38.050
have too much free time, don't I?

15:38.550 --> 15:40.790
How about I introduce someone to you?

15:41.790 --> 15:43.340
I've been waiting for you to say that.

15:43.390 --> 15:43.800
Okay.

15:43.830 --> 15:44.780
We've known each other for so long,

15:44.800 --> 15:46.860
you should have introduced someone to me long ago.

15:46.860 --> 15:48.070
What type do you like?

15:49.070 --> 15:49.910
Hurry up.

15:50.420 --> 15:51.390
I forgot my phone.

15:51.390 --> 15:52.340
Have you finished signing?

15:52.740 --> 15:53.850
I... I'm done.

15:54.020 --> 15:54.540
Let's go.

16:25.550 --> 16:26.580
Is Liu Xiaoming here?

16:27.100 --> 16:27.730
Yes.

16:32.980 --> 16:33.810
He.

16:33.950 --> 16:36.270
Auntie, did you take time off to come here?

16:36.550 --> 16:36.980
Yes.

16:37.550 --> 16:39.390
Didn't you tell Professor Yu

16:39.390 --> 16:40.620
that I need a checkup?

16:40.950 --> 16:44.390
I did it, and the results are out. I want to let you have a look.

16:44.390 --> 16:45.580
Alright, I'll take a look.

16:55.550 --> 16:57.190
The other items look pretty good,

16:57.580 --> 16:59.270
except for a breast nodule on the left side.

16:59.700 --> 17:00.580
The doctor,

17:00.580 --> 17:02.310
when doing the ultrasound for me,

17:02.610 --> 17:03.760
had a concerned expression.

17:05.020 --> 17:06.460
It made me quite worried.

17:07.500 --> 17:09.010
This breast nodule of yours,

17:09.339 --> 17:11.540
indeed needs further examination.

17:12.540 --> 17:13.670
Is it very serious

17:14.369 --> 17:15.170
that I need to check further?

17:15.780 --> 17:16.630
Don't worry.

17:17.109 --> 17:19.300
For women in their forties and fifties,

17:19.300 --> 17:21.300
it's indeed crucial to pay close attention to breast health.

17:21.700 --> 17:22.589
So,

17:22.589 --> 17:24.220
we have to do further tests

17:24.220 --> 17:26.060
to provide a definitive diagnosis.

17:29.540 --> 17:31.500
Actually, I've always been in good health,

17:31.500 --> 17:33.220
and I haven't felt any discomfort anywhere.

17:33.900 --> 17:35.660
It surely can't be breast cancer.

17:38.300 --> 17:39.020
Alright,

17:39.390 --> 17:40.260
I'll follow your advice.

17:40.840 --> 17:41.700
What examinations do I need to undergo?

17:41.700 --> 17:42.700
I'll fully cooperate.

17:43.150 --> 17:44.650
I've already taken a day off anyway.

17:44.910 --> 17:45.580
How about this?

17:45.910 --> 17:48.500
Let's do all the examinations to be at ease.

17:50.020 --> 17:52.350
Okay, I'll write you a prescription.

17:52.830 --> 17:53.980
There will be a few minor examinations shortly.

17:53.980 --> 17:55.300
I'll have a student escort you there.

18:06.250 --> 18:09.650
[Medical Examination for tumor]

18:17.980 --> 18:18.670
Okay.

18:19.670 --> 18:20.980
Please guide Mrs. Shen to her examinations.

18:20.980 --> 18:21.390
Alright.

18:22.540 --> 18:23.740
Sorry for the trouble.

18:24.020 --> 18:24.700
Don't worry.

18:24.700 --> 18:25.430
Okay.

18:43.870 --> 18:44.630
Make sure to get plenty of rest

18:44.630 --> 18:45.950
and cut down on alcohol.

18:45.950 --> 18:46.430
Thank you, doctor.

18:46.430 --> 18:47.110
It's fine.

18:58.700 --> 19:01.500
I found another one of the same kind in the corner of the cabinet.

19:13.350 --> 19:16.820
Your mom came to the hospital.

19:49.950 --> 19:50.880
I have one here too.

20:10.350 --> 20:10.910
Come in.

20:13.980 --> 20:14.670
Senior He,

20:14.670 --> 20:16.020
Ms. Liu's test results are out.

20:16.590 --> 20:17.260
Please have a seat, Auntie.

20:38.220 --> 20:39.260
Is it a tumour?

20:46.020 --> 20:48.430
Based on the examination report and ultrasound,

20:51.020 --> 20:52.300
there's a high probability it's a tumour.

20:55.540 --> 20:56.780
So it's breast cancer then.

20:58.580 --> 20:59.650
It's only a high probability,

21:00.110 --> 21:01.590
and it could also be benign.

21:04.700 --> 21:06.140
But it could also be malignant.

21:13.590 --> 21:14.980
Don't worry, Auntie.

21:15.500 --> 21:17.110
Whether it's benign or malignant

21:17.350 --> 21:18.900
can only be determined through a biopsy.

21:22.110 --> 21:22.980
How is it done?

21:24.540 --> 21:26.430
We can do a needle biopsy,

21:27.150 --> 21:28.590
or a surgical biopsy.

21:29.700 --> 21:31.780
The needle biopsy has a smaller incision,

21:32.500 --> 21:33.870
while with the surgical biopsy,

21:33.870 --> 21:35.460
we can remove the lump

21:35.770 --> 21:38.160
and perform a rapid pathology test for a definitive diagnosis.

21:38.220 --> 21:39.670
Then, based on the diagnosis,

21:39.670 --> 21:41.640
decide on the subsequent surgical approach.

21:42.060 --> 21:43.220
If the results are good,

21:43.220 --> 21:44.260
we can directly suture the incision,

21:45.260 --> 21:46.690
avoiding any secondary harm.

21:48.430 --> 21:49.740
When you say removal,

21:50.460 --> 21:52.510
do you mean removing the entire breast?

21:52.900 --> 21:53.710
No.

21:54.060 --> 21:55.430
It's possible to avoid removing the breast.

22:05.300 --> 22:06.060
Needle biopsy

22:06.700 --> 22:07.670
or removal,

22:11.260 --> 22:12.110
I don't understand either.

22:13.500 --> 22:14.210
I don't...

22:14.430 --> 22:15.460
I don't understand all this.

22:19.980 --> 22:20.870
How about this then?

22:21.460 --> 22:23.280
How about you notify Uncle and Xifan first,

22:23.500 --> 22:25.590
so they can discuss it with you?

22:28.630 --> 22:29.870
They're not doctors,

22:30.790 --> 22:31.940
what advice could they give?

22:39.910 --> 22:40.800
He,

22:42.500 --> 22:43.450
you're a doctor.

22:44.390 --> 22:45.430
I'll listen to you.

22:46.110 --> 22:47.220
What do you suggest?

22:55.260 --> 22:56.110
I recommend

22:57.390 --> 22:58.430
surgical treatment.

23:06.060 --> 23:06.760
Surgery.

23:09.220 --> 23:09.830
Okay.

23:10.290 --> 23:11.400
Then I'll arrange it for you directly.

23:12.150 --> 23:14.040
If all goes well, you can be admitted to the hospital tomorrow.

23:14.150 --> 23:15.670
The surgery can be performed the day after tomorrow.

23:16.760 --> 23:17.670
That's so fast.

23:27.540 --> 23:28.210
Auntie,

23:28.780 --> 23:30.060
I still suggest that you

23:30.060 --> 23:31.950
inform Uncle and Xifan first.

23:32.830 --> 23:34.260
After all, before and after the surgery,

23:34.300 --> 23:36.190
you'll need family to take care of you during your hospital stay.

23:39.290 --> 23:40.810
I'll tell Mr. Shen.

23:41.980 --> 23:42.820
As for Ms. Shen,

23:44.350 --> 23:45.460
keep it a secret for me.

23:47.540 --> 23:48.740
That doesn't seem right.

23:49.190 --> 23:49.740
I...

23:51.020 --> 23:53.220
I want to wait until the pathology report comes out before telling her.

23:53.980 --> 23:55.430
What if it's really benign?

23:55.940 --> 23:57.750
Wouldn't she be worrying for nothing?

24:01.820 --> 24:02.970
This morning,

24:03.370 --> 24:05.200
as soon as I got that medical report,

24:05.260 --> 24:06.910
you were the first person I thought of.

24:08.430 --> 24:09.830
I think you're the most reliable,

24:10.590 --> 24:12.460
and trustworthy person.

24:14.430 --> 24:15.220
Promise me,

24:17.430 --> 24:18.390
you won't tell her.

24:28.140 --> 24:28.730
Alright.

24:49.950 --> 24:50.780
He Suye.

24:59.060 --> 24:59.870
What's wrong?

25:01.260 --> 25:02.020
Nothing.

25:02.160 --> 25:02.860
Do you want a drink?

25:03.040 --> 25:04.230
No need, I can just drink this.

25:06.630 --> 25:07.700
Are you okay?

25:07.700 --> 25:09.260
You seem to be in a bad mood.

25:10.260 --> 25:12.460
It's nothing, I'm just thinking about some work-related matters.

25:14.590 --> 25:15.500
Why don't you go sit for a while?

25:16.430 --> 25:17.350
I'll join you in a bit.

25:30.460 --> 25:31.870
You went to the hospital this afternoon?

25:32.500 --> 25:34.190
Why didn't you tell me to go with you?

25:34.910 --> 25:35.690
I originally thought

25:35.720 --> 25:37.510
it was just a slightly larger nodule.

25:38.350 --> 25:39.300
And you had classes,

25:40.350 --> 25:41.430
so I went by myself.

25:42.190 --> 25:42.590
No,

25:44.430 --> 25:45.950
why do they want you to be hospitalized?

25:47.460 --> 25:48.630
He said

25:49.930 --> 25:51.060
it's definitely a tumor,

25:51.520 --> 25:53.630
so they need to perform surgery to remove it

25:54.260 --> 25:55.350
and then do a biopsy

25:55.780 --> 25:56.790
to confirm

25:56.810 --> 25:58.640
whether it's malignant or benign.

25:59.620 --> 26:00.930
No, it's...

26:03.300 --> 26:04.780
That's not what I'm thinking about now.

26:05.980 --> 26:06.950
What I'm thinking is

26:07.630 --> 26:09.950
how to tell our daughter that I have to be hospitalized.

26:10.460 --> 26:11.670
I don't want her to know.

26:12.950 --> 26:13.630
No, she...

26:14.540 --> 26:15.280
Then you...

26:15.530 --> 26:16.770
You tell me

26:17.590 --> 26:19.950
how are you going to hide this from her?

26:20.210 --> 26:22.820
We don't know if it's malignant or benign yet.

26:23.190 --> 26:24.260
Why tell her then?

26:25.150 --> 26:26.780
Wouldn't that just make her worry for nothing?

26:30.740 --> 26:32.190
If I'm unlucky,

26:32.750 --> 26:34.220
and it turns out to be malignant,

26:38.350 --> 26:39.630
then it's breast cancer.

26:41.350 --> 26:41.540
No.

26:41.540 --> 26:42.900
It's a sure thing.

26:44.540 --> 26:45.930
We can let her know anytime then, can't we?

26:46.260 --> 26:46.780
No, that's not it.

26:46.780 --> 26:47.460
Don't...

26:48.110 --> 26:48.590
Don't...

26:50.060 --> 26:51.150
Don't panic yet.

26:51.150 --> 26:51.700
I...

26:52.110 --> 26:52.830
I'll think of something.

26:52.830 --> 26:53.950
I'll figure out how to

26:53.950 --> 26:54.980
talk to her about it.

26:55.500 --> 26:56.590
The key now is

26:56.590 --> 26:57.980
It's not even a holiday now,

26:57.980 --> 26:59.390
so we can't say we're going

26:59.390 --> 27:00.190
on a trip.

27:03.220 --> 27:03.630
No.

27:03.630 --> 27:04.020
Why...

27:04.020 --> 27:06.060
Why is this so sudden?

27:09.630 --> 27:10.700
It's not that sudden actually.

27:11.980 --> 27:13.190
I don't blame anyone.

27:14.870 --> 27:15.910
I only blame myself.

27:18.150 --> 27:19.550
I should have gone for a check-up earlier.

27:22.150 --> 27:23.460
Don't cry, don't cry.

27:24.150 --> 27:25.870
It'll be fine, I'm sure.

27:29.910 --> 27:30.460
Don't worry.

27:30.460 --> 27:31.500
I'm here.

27:33.150 --> 27:34.630
Fortune favors the virtuous.

27:34.630 --> 27:35.700
Everything will be alright.

27:56.300 --> 27:56.850
Here.

27:57.110 --> 27:58.210
The medicine is warmed up.

28:00.740 --> 28:01.300
By the way,

28:01.300 --> 28:01.950
Ms. Shen,

28:02.780 --> 28:03.780
your mother's team at work

28:03.780 --> 28:05.780
is going to the neighboring city for training tomorrow.

28:06.460 --> 28:08.040
I've rescheduled a few classes,

28:08.390 --> 28:10.700
hoping to tag along with her for a couple of days.

28:11.670 --> 28:13.870
Alright, you two have a good time.

28:13.870 --> 28:14.910
Okay.

28:38.560 --> 28:39.470
Uncle, Auntie.

28:39.540 --> 28:40.670
Have you been waiting long?

28:40.670 --> 28:42.560
-No.
-Let's go, Auntie.

28:43.780 --> 28:45.150
Let's handle the hospital admission procedures first.

28:45.150 --> 28:45.870
Yes, it's right over there.

28:45.870 --> 28:46.390
Okay, okay.

28:50.210 --> 28:51.580
Uncle, Auntie, you rest first.

28:51.600 --> 28:52.800
I'll come find you later.

28:52.830 --> 28:53.950
Alright, thank you.

28:57.250 --> 28:58.380
Please follow me, both of you.

29:02.700 --> 29:03.430
Who is it?

29:03.950 --> 29:05.300
My girlfriend's parents.

29:05.300 --> 29:06.460
Please help to take care of them.

29:07.590 --> 29:08.870
Alright, don't worry.

29:09.010 --> 29:10.450
I've got it covered.

29:19.440 --> 29:19.920
I'll leave now.

29:23.590 --> 29:24.450
A little lower then.

29:24.470 --> 29:25.360
Okay.

29:25.870 --> 29:26.500
Uncle, Auntie.

29:26.500 --> 29:27.300
He.

29:27.910 --> 29:29.500
This is Director Zhou from the surgery department.

29:30.300 --> 29:30.950
Hello.

29:31.260 --> 29:32.670
I'm the lead surgeon for tomorrow's operation.

29:32.670 --> 29:33.460
My surname is Zhou.

29:34.150 --> 29:35.430
I came to see you today first.

29:37.540 --> 29:38.060
Oh, right.

29:38.630 --> 29:42.020
this is Ms. Liu's Surgical Informed Consent Form.

29:42.250 --> 29:43.250
We need a family member to sign it.

29:43.540 --> 29:44.260
Please take a look.

29:52.830 --> 29:53.500
This...

29:58.670 --> 29:59.390
This...

30:00.630 --> 30:03.110
Don't worry. Although it's a removal surgery,

30:03.110 --> 30:04.740
the technique is already very mature.

30:04.740 --> 30:05.700
There shouldn't be any problems.

30:06.980 --> 30:08.110
Okay, okay.

30:10.160 --> 30:10.570
Here.

30:10.590 --> 30:11.390
Thank you.

30:12.830 --> 30:13.830
I've taken a look.

30:14.190 --> 30:15.830
The tumor is located on the left side.

30:16.150 --> 30:18.110
Can you feel it yourself usually?

30:21.430 --> 30:22.540
Also,

30:22.540 --> 30:23.460
do you usually feel

30:23.460 --> 30:25.020
some discomfort in your armpit?

30:26.460 --> 30:28.020
A little bit, occasionally.

30:28.910 --> 30:30.110
I roughly know now.

30:31.830 --> 30:32.300
Thank you.

30:32.870 --> 30:35.070
Okay, the operation is tomorrow.

30:35.190 --> 30:36.630
Get some rest early tonight.

30:37.110 --> 30:38.150
No need to be too nervous.

30:38.430 --> 30:39.430
Try to relax.

30:40.110 --> 30:40.910
He,

30:41.190 --> 30:42.390
I'll go attend to my duties now.

30:42.540 --> 30:43.150
Okay.

30:43.150 --> 30:44.320
If you need anything, come find me in my office.

30:44.780 --> 30:45.300
Thank you for your hard work.

30:45.300 --> 30:45.910
Thank you.

30:45.910 --> 30:46.700
You're welcome.

30:52.150 --> 30:53.700
Later, a nurse will come to

30:53.700 --> 30:55.910
explain some pre and post-operative precautions to you.

30:56.490 --> 30:58.820
If you have any other questions, feel free to ask me anytime.

31:00.460 --> 31:02.980
Take good care of Ms. Shen these two days.

31:04.800 --> 31:06.150
Okay, don't worry.

31:07.630 --> 31:08.400
Alright.

31:08.450 --> 31:09.570
You've gone to so much trouble, really.

31:09.590 --> 31:11.150
You've been helping us arrange everything.

31:11.150 --> 31:12.020
We really...

31:12.020 --> 31:13.220
I just did what I should.

31:14.860 --> 31:15.380
Alright.

31:16.590 --> 31:17.550
Thank you, He.

31:20.670 --> 31:22.300
Then you rest first.

31:22.300 --> 31:22.540
Okay.

31:22.540 --> 31:23.220
I'll go back to work now.

31:24.150 --> 31:25.350
Thank you, thank you.

31:35.060 --> 31:35.740
It's nothing.

31:35.740 --> 31:36.830
The doctor said,

31:37.460 --> 31:38.500
keep a calm mindset.

32:02.020 --> 32:03.110
Family members wait outside.

32:03.700 --> 32:05.190
Okay, thank you.

32:05.740 --> 32:08.430
[Surgical Patient Entrance]

32:44.710 --> 32:45.390
He.

32:45.870 --> 32:46.940
The rapid pathology results are out.

32:47.500 --> 32:48.300
It's malignant.

32:48.620 --> 32:49.790
Fortunately, it hasn't metastasized yet.

32:51.480 --> 32:53.080
So what should we do next?

32:53.210 --> 32:55.340
It hasn't spread to the sentinel lymph nodes yet.

32:55.670 --> 32:57.150
But to prevent spreading,

32:57.220 --> 32:58.870
we need to expand the scope of the surgery a bit,

32:58.870 --> 32:59.980
just to be safe.

33:00.300 --> 33:02.150
So, you can consider

33:02.150 --> 33:03.980
whether to opt for breast-conserving surgery or a full mastectomy?

33:08.820 --> 33:09.410
Let's conserve.

33:11.390 --> 33:12.150
Let's go with breast conservation.

33:12.590 --> 33:13.950
Breast conservation is better

33:13.950 --> 33:14.950
for the patient's mental health.

33:15.430 --> 33:17.360
Okay, we'll do the breast-conserving surgery then.

33:17.510 --> 33:19.270
Family members, please don't worry too much.

33:20.170 --> 33:21.580
No metastasis is good news.

33:21.600 --> 33:23.400
Fortunately, we found out it in time.

33:25.020 --> 33:25.950
He, I'll go attend to other matters now.

33:26.350 --> 33:26.780
Thank you.

33:26.780 --> 33:27.300
You're welcome.

33:31.460 --> 33:32.100
He, this...

33:32.100 --> 33:32.740
How...

33:32.740 --> 33:33.630
How did it turn out to be...

33:33.630 --> 33:34.980
m-malignant?

33:34.980 --> 33:36.700
It hasn't been metasized yet. Don't worry.

33:44.050 --> 33:45.910
[Oncology Ward (2)]

34:12.830 --> 34:14.830
Auntie, does your wound still hurt?

34:16.389 --> 34:17.179
It's fine.

34:18.949 --> 34:19.790
Don't worry.

34:20.020 --> 34:21.179
You're only in the early stages.

34:21.429 --> 34:23.800
The wound is small and will heal quickly.

34:26.659 --> 34:28.659
I'll write you a prescription in a moment,

34:28.659 --> 34:29.780
for tonifying qi and nourishing blood.

34:29.949 --> 34:31.139
Drink it to help with recovery.

34:31.300 --> 34:32.610
You'll be able to leave the hospital in a couple of days.

34:34.350 --> 34:35.270
That's good.

34:35.750 --> 34:36.900
By the way, Dr. He,

34:37.010 --> 34:38.790
what about the follow-up treatment?

34:39.659 --> 34:40.580
It will take about two weeks

34:40.580 --> 34:41.980
for the full pathology report to come out.

34:42.600 --> 34:44.159
Then, based on the pathology report,

34:44.580 --> 34:46.179
we'll arrange the subsequent treatment methods.

34:46.429 --> 34:46.830
We need...

34:47.460 --> 34:48.949
We need two weeks?

34:49.830 --> 34:51.179
We can't rush this.

34:53.659 --> 34:55.790
During this time, just keep a calm mindset.

34:55.790 --> 34:56.870
Live well,

34:57.210 --> 34:58.480
and do some appropriate work out.

34:58.950 --> 35:01.260
This is to build a good foundation for the subsequent treatment.

35:03.430 --> 35:04.430
Subsequent treatment

35:05.710 --> 35:07.500
would be radiotherapy,

35:08.060 --> 35:09.460
chemotherapy, and such, right?

35:13.350 --> 35:15.180
Will I lose my hair,

35:16.140 --> 35:17.180
not be able to eat,

35:17.750 --> 35:19.500
and feel nauseous and vomit?

35:20.430 --> 35:22.800
Auntie, the pathology report isn't out yet.

35:22.980 --> 35:23.980
Don't overthink it.

35:25.910 --> 35:27.060
Yes.

35:28.710 --> 35:29.950
The doctor has already said,

35:30.460 --> 35:31.620
keep a calm mindset,

35:52.340 --> 35:53.300
Don't worry, Auntie.

35:55.540 --> 35:56.390
I'm here.

35:57.150 --> 35:58.980
I'll definitely give you the best treatment plan.

37:08.350 --> 37:09.430
What are you thinking about?

37:09.750 --> 37:11.420
You didn't even notice me coming in.

37:12.910 --> 37:15.710
I... I was thinking about the lesson plans

37:31.660 --> 37:32.830
Sir, the payment has been made.

37:32.830 --> 37:34.350
Alright, just a moment.

37:41.540 --> 37:42.270
What's wrong?

37:42.270 --> 37:43.250
You look upset.

37:45.430 --> 37:46.910
Mr. Shen and Ms. Liu

37:46.910 --> 37:48.710
are both not responding to my messages.

37:48.730 --> 37:49.920
I don't know what they're up to.

37:53.230 --> 37:53.950
Don't worry.

37:54.270 --> 37:56.060
They should be fine.

37:56.750 --> 37:57.870
I'm not worried.

37:58.270 --> 37:59.310
I'm just wondering if

37:59.310 --> 38:01.180
those two are having too much fun

38:01.180 --> 38:02.230
and have forgotten about me?

38:03.020 --> 38:04.060
How could that be?

38:04.060 --> 38:05.000
Don't overthink it.

38:14.540 --> 38:15.460
Here you go.

38:15.460 --> 38:16.540
Thank you, sir.

38:17.140 --> 38:17.980
Here, take it.

38:17.980 --> 38:18.870
Thank you.

38:19.350 --> 38:19.910
Let's go.

38:20.140 --> 38:20.910
That hand.

38:36.830 --> 38:38.750
I'll come back to check your temperature in two hours.

38:39.310 --> 38:40.390
Get some rest.

38:47.350 --> 38:48.180
Caifang,

38:48.580 --> 38:50.790
why do you look so worried after coming back from the ward?

38:51.660 --> 38:52.950
Isn't that Dr. He's

38:52.950 --> 38:54.370
girlfriend's parents?

38:54.500 --> 38:55.790
I need to take extra care of them.

38:56.620 --> 38:58.270
Manager Shen's parents?

38:58.970 --> 39:00.050
You don't know?

39:00.790 --> 39:03.230
Her mother is hospitalized for a removal surgery.

39:04.230 --> 39:05.540
But it's strange.

39:05.540 --> 39:07.090
Why hasn't she shown up even once?

39:19.060 --> 39:20.630
The rapid pathology shows malignancy.

39:21.060 --> 39:22.660
We're still waiting for the full pathology report.

39:24.950 --> 39:25.710
I know.

39:27.460 --> 39:28.620
Once the full pathology report is out,

39:28.620 --> 39:30.580
we'll provide a treatment plan immediately.

39:33.500 --> 39:33.980
Okay.

39:34.350 --> 39:35.310
Got it, Grandpa.

39:36.020 --> 39:36.830
Bye-bye.

39:41.040 --> 39:41.880
Thank you.

39:44.790 --> 39:45.540
Suye,

39:46.100 --> 39:49.500
I heard that Manager Shen's mother is sick and hospitalized.

39:53.700 --> 39:55.700
No wonder I've seen you running back and forth these past two days.

39:56.500 --> 39:58.730
With you around, Manager Shen doesn't need to worry at all.

40:01.910 --> 40:02.710
She...

40:04.440 --> 40:05.480
She doesn't know yet.

40:09.790 --> 40:11.020
Before the results come out,

40:11.310 --> 40:12.580
Auntie doesn't want me to tell her.

40:13.060 --> 40:13.980
I have no choice.

40:14.620 --> 40:15.950
That's not good, is it?

40:16.870 --> 40:17.790
Her mother is sick,

40:17.790 --> 40:18.910
and they're not telling the daughter?

40:19.270 --> 40:20.620
I know what you mean,

40:21.060 --> 40:22.430
but I can also understand Auntie.

40:22.870 --> 40:24.430
She doesn't want Xifan to worry.

40:24.910 --> 40:26.140
That's still not good.

40:27.100 --> 40:28.060
No matter how understandable it is,

40:28.060 --> 40:29.690
Manager Shen is the one directly involved.

40:29.830 --> 40:32.020
If she knows she's been kept in the dark,

40:32.170 --> 40:33.690
she'll definitely be very upset.

40:34.270 --> 40:35.980
After all, it's her own mother.

40:36.410 --> 40:37.870
What will happen when she finds out later?

40:38.100 --> 40:39.610
She'll surely regret it.

40:40.100 --> 40:40.700
Really?

40:40.730 --> 40:41.830
Are you not going to tell her?
